    <briefdescription>
<para>Battery Management Service (BMS) public API. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This service manages high-level battery behavior for the EPS, including:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>pack voltage/current monitoring</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>temperature and health estimation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>charge state determination</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>enabling/disabling charging/balancing circuits</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>protection and failsafe behavior</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>telemetry collection for upstream consumption</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>error state management by notifying redundancy manager</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>The BMS interacts with HAL drivers to obtain sensor readings, and provides state for use by the power policy application. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
